message.content:
```json
{
  "endpoint_path": "/api/weth/transfers",
  "description": "Get recent WETH transfers with optional address filtering and pagination",
  "method": "GET",
  "path_params": [],
  "query_params": [
    {"name": "address", "type": "Option<String>", "description": "Filter transfers by source or destination address", "default": "null"},
    {"name": "limit", "type": "u32", "description": "Maximum number of transfers to return", "default": 50},
    {"name": "startBlockTimestamp", "type": "Option<u64>", "description": "Filter transfers occurring after this timestamp", "default": "null"}
  ],
  "response_schema": {
    "name": "WethTransferResponse",
    "fields": [
      {"name": "block_number", "type": "i64", "description": "Block number where the transfer occurred"},
      {"name": "block_timestamp", "type": "i64", "description": "Unix timestamp of the block containing the transfer"},
      {"name": "transaction_hash", "type": "String", "description": "Hash of the transaction containing the transfer"},
      {"name": "log_index", "type": "i32", "description": "Log index within the block for the transfer event"},
      {"name": "src", "type": "String", "description": "Source address of the transfer"},
      {"name": "dst", "type": "String", "description": "Destination address of the transfer"},
      {"name": "wad", "type": "String", "description": "Amount of WETH transferred"}
    ]
  },
  "sql_query": "\n    SELECT block_number, block_timestamp, transaction_hash, log_index, src, dst, wad\n    FROM weth_transfers\n    WHERE ($1::VARCHAR IS NULL OR src = $1 OR dst = $1)\n    AND ($2::BIGINT IS NULL OR block_timestamp >= $2)\n    ORDER BY block_timestamp DESC\n    LIMIT $3\n  ",
  "tables_referenced": ["weth_transfers"]
}
```
